        <div id="content" class="editable"><h1>About The Council</h1>
<p>The DoD Regional Councils for Small Business Education and Advocacy are a nationwide network of small business specialists organized to promote the&nbsp;Small Business Programs.&nbsp;The&nbsp;Northeast Regional Council (NERC) covers New England and New York state.&nbsp;</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<h1><span style="color: #993300;">Mission</span></h1>
<p><strong>Promote Small Business Utilization</strong></p>
<p>The Council advances the mission of&nbsp;small business utilization&nbsp;by hosting Matchmaker and Training&nbsp;Events&nbsp;throughout our region. The Matchmaker Event brings together small businesses, representatives of Federal agencies and large prime contractors for dialogue between buyer and seller that may lead to a long term business relationship. Understanding the needs of Federal agencies and Federal prime contractors is the first step small businesses can take in becoming a government contractor.</p>
<p><strong>Provide Training</strong></p>
<p>The Council also has developed training for both small businesses and for prime contractors which are provided the day prior to the Matchmaker. Our training provides the forum to learn and to network with others with shared goals in the contracting community. The current training modules can be accessed from the “Learning Center” tab. The training and resources that the Council has developed&nbsp;enhance small business participation in Federal prime contracts &amp; subcontracts and are routinely updated to reflect current regulations.</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<h1><span style="color: #993300;">Membership</span></h1>
<ul>
<li>
<p>Small Business&nbsp;Specialists from DoD&nbsp;and all Federal civilian agencies</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>Small Business Liaison Officers (SBLOs) and other small business advocates from large&nbsp;prime contractors&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>Procurement Technical Assistance Centers (PTACs)</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p>If you are interested in becoming a member of the&nbsp;Council, <a title="Link to contact us page" href="http://dodneregional.org/contact_us/contact_us.html" target="_self">Click Here</a> to contact us.</p></div>
